data.name: Button2.Text
data.value:
The application is a game made for an entertaining experience. Visual Vagrant is a hybrid between a text based game (Dungeon Man 2.0) and an open world, top down adventure game (The Legend of Zelda).
Players are faced with the tasks of having to survive by obtaining water, encountering enemies with different mini-games (each opening a separate form).
The game is used for a simple and meaningful narrative experience. As a heavily text-based game, players are able to experience a story while navigating through different mechanics, composed of various code structures.
The end-user of this application will be the demographic of gamers, both casual and dedicated. Due to our simple and straightforward interface and control mechanics, anyone who is willing to immerse themselves in the game can learn how to play without difficulty in comprehension.
The game is compatible with text-to-speech/screen reader software peripherals.
